title: Bob Dylan - Ten Of Swords (Rare LPs 61-65)
description:
'Ten of Swords' is a ten-LP set of Dylan material from 1961-1966. 
Here we have nine of them from 1961-1965. 
We left out the so-called 'Albert Hall Concert' 
which is available in many other ways.
Released in the summer of 1985, shortly before the release 
of 'Biograph' later that autumn, several rock journalists 
declared Ten of Swords to be the more important release.
